trans-unit.source: Converts the <xref href="System.Windows.Window.DialogResult"></xref> property, which is a <xref href="System.Nullable`1"></xref> value of type <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref>, to and from other types.
XAML Text Usage
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> class.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from other types to <xref href="System.Windows.Window.DialogResult"></xref> (a <xref href="System.Nullable`1"></xref> value of type <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref>).
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
A <xref href="System.Type"></xref> that represents the type to convert from.
A <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref> that always returns `false`.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from <xref href="System.Windows.Window.DialogResult"></xref> (a <xref href="System.Nullable`1"></xref> value of type <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref>) to other types.
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
A <xref href="System.Type"></xref> that represents the type to convert to.
A <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref> that always returns `false`.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from <xref href="System.Windows.Window.DialogResult"></xref> (a <xref href="System.Nullable`1"></xref> value of type <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref>) to other types.
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
The <xref href="System.Globalization.CultureInfo"></xref> to use as the current culture.
If `null` is passed, the current culture is assumed.
The <xref href="System.Object"></xref> to convert.
Always raises <xref href="System.InvalidOperationException"></xref>.
<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter.ConvertFrom(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext,System.Globalization.CultureInfo,System.Object)"></xref> is called.

<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter"></xref> does not support converting from other types to <xref href="System.Windows.Window.DialogResult"></xref> (a <xref href="System.Nullable`1"></xref> value of type <xref href="System.Boolean"></xref>).
A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides a format context.
The <xref href="System.Globalization.CultureInfo"></xref> to use as the current culture.
If `null` is passed, the current culture is assumed.
The <xref href="System.Object"></xref> to convert.
The <xref href="System.Type"></xref> to convert the value parameter to.
Always raises <xref href="System.InvalidOperationException"></xref>.
<xref href="System.Windows.DialogResultConverter.CanConvertTo(System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext,System.Type)"></xref> is called.
